Sanguine			KEY:Oracle ~ Sanguine					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:OracleClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.OracleCurse															DEFINE:OracleSanguineCurseBonus|0	BONUS:VAR|OracleSanguineCurseBonus|(1+(OracleCurseLVL/5))		DESC:You are slow to recognize adversity or danger, although your optimism can be contagious. You take a -5 penalty to Perception checks to notice opponents or traps and to Sense Motive checks. You cannot be demoralized, and during surprise rounds and against traps, you gain a +%1 luck bonus to AC and saving throws. Your luck bonus increases by +1 every five curse levels.|OracleSanguineCurseBonus																																																																																																										BONUS:SITUATION|Perception=Notice opponents or traps|-5	BONUS:SKILL|Sense Motive|-5	TEMPBONUS:PC|COMBAT|AC|OracleSanguineCurseBonus|TYPE=Luck	TEMPBONUS:PC|SAVE|ALL|OracleSanguineCurseBonus|TYPE=Luck																																																		DESC:You gain aura of courage, as a paladin.|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5																																																																																																																																																																																	ABILITY:Special Ability|VIRTUAL|Paladin ~ Aura of Courage|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5																																																																																																																																																																																						DESC:When your wounds would normally make you unconscious, you become staggered and remain conscious for one round.|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,10																																																																																																																			DESC:You gain immunity to compulsion spells and spell-like abilities. Each ally within 10 feet of you gains a +4 morale bonus on saving throws against compulsion effects. This ability functions only while you are conscious, not if you are unconscious or dead.|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,15	SOURCEPAGE:p.5
Sedentary			KEY:Oracle ~ Sedentary					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:OracleClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.OracleCurse																																								DESC:You are locked inside your body, barely able to move. Divine powers have wracked your bones and nerves, filling you with power and insight but diminishing your mobility. Your movement rate is 5 feet, and your Strength and Dexterity are effectively no higher than your curse level for the purposes of skill checks, attack rolls, and saving throws. However, you can cast mage hand and open/close as orisons, in addition to your usual spells, and you may treat your Dexterity modifier to initiative as though it were equal to your Charisma modifier. You may roll twice when you make a Will save, taking the better result, %1 times per day, but no more than once per saving throw.|(CHA+1)																																	BONUS:MOVEADD|Type.Walk|5-MOVEBASE	BONUS:SKILL|STAT.STR|(min(STR,OracleCurseLVL)-STR)	BONUS:SKILL|STAT.DEX|(min(DEX,OracleCurseLVL)-DEX)	BONUS:COMBAT|TOHIT.Melee|(min(STR,OracleCurseLVL)-STR)	BONUS:COMBAT|TOHIT.Ranged|(min(DEX,OracleCurseLVL)-DEX)	BONUS:SAVE|Reflex|(min(DEX,OracleCurseLVL)-DEX)	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=0|Mage Hand,Open/Close	BONUS:COMBAT|INITIATIVE|(max(CHA,DEX)-DEX)																																																																																																																																																																																																						SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=2|Spiritual Weapon|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=5|Telekinesis|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,10																																																																																																																																			SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=7|Scrying (Greater)|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,15	SOURCEPAGE:p.5
Unchained			KEY:Oracle ~ Unchained					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:OracleClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.OracleCurse																																								DESC:Some force has severed you from the normal realms of morality and ethics. Freedom can be a burden, and angels and devils alike mistrust you. You have no aura for spells that detect alignment, such as detect evil. You suffer a -2 circumstance penalty with Charisma-based skills against outsiders with an alignment subtype. Casting a spell on you that gives you an illusory alignment aura requires a Concentration check with a DC of 10+double the spells level or the spell fails.																																																																																																																																																																																									DESC:You have no alignment. You can become a member of any class, even one with an alignment requirement, and can never lose your membership because of a change in alignment. If you violate the code of ethics of any of your classes, you might still lose access to certain features of such classes, subject to GM discretion. Attempts to detect your alignment don’t return any results. If a class restricts you from casting spells with an alignment descriptor, you can cast such spells without restrictions or repercussions. If you’re the target of a spell or effect that is based on alignment, you’re treated as the most favorable alignment when determining the spell’s effect on you. Any effects that alter alignment have no effect on you.|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5				BONUS:VAR|BypassClassAlignment_All_Class|1||TYPE=Bypass|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=5|Break Enchantment|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,10																																																																																																																																	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Unchained Oracle Spell Choice|1|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,15	SOURCEPAGE:p.5
Waking Dreamer		KEY:Oracle ~ Waking Dreamer				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:OracleClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.OracleCurse																																								DESC:You are drowsy and afflicted by fleeting hallucinations. You take a -5 to Perception checks and take a -2 penalty to save versus illusions. However, you are immune to sleep effects.																																																																																																																																																															BONUS:SKILL|Perception|-5																																																																																														DESC:Add Sleep and Hypnotism to your spells known.|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5																																																																																																																																																																																SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=1|Sleep,Hypnotism|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5																																																																																																																																																																																										DESC:Add Dream to your spells known.|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,10																																																																																							SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=5|Dream|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,10																																	DESC:Add Project Image to your spells known.|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,15																																																																																	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=7|Project Image|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,15	SOURCEPAGE:p.5
Wan					KEY:Oracle ~ Wan						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:OracleClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.OracleCurse																																								DESC:You are pale, sickly, and languorous, with one foot in death’s door. You have the fatigued condition, but are immune to the exhausted condition.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												DESC:You learn the “inflict” spell of any level spell you can cast.|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5																																																																																																																																																																												SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=1|Inflict Light Wounds|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=2|Inflict Moderate Wounds|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=4|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=3|Inflict Serious Wounds|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=6|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=4|Inflict Critical Wounds|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=8|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=5|Inflict Light Wounds (Mass)|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=10|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=6|Inflict Moderate Wounds (Mass)|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=12|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=7|Inflict Serious Wounds (Mass)|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=14|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=8|Inflict Critical Wounds (Mass)|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=16|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,5																																																																																																										SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=3|Ray of Exhaustion|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,10																																																																																																																																	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Oracle=7|Waves of Exhaustion|PREVARGTEQ:OracleCurseLVL,15	S